   "source": [
    "# How to create and visualize quadrics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os, sys\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, os.path.abspath(\"..\"))\n",
    "\n",
    "import geoclide as gc"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"

     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "disk = gc.Disk(radius=1.)\n",
    "disk.plot(color='green', edgecolor='k')\n",
    "annulus = gc.Disk(radius=1., inner_radius=0.5)\n",
    "annulus.plot(color='green', edgecolor='k')\n",
    "partial_annulus = gc.Disk(radius=1., inner_radius=0.5, phi_max=270)\n",
    "partial_annulus.plot(color='green', edgecolor='k')"
   ]
  },
